Authors: Albert Paez | albertzeap@gmail.com

*******************************************************************

Language: Python

*******************************************************************
About: 
	This program uses tkinter GUI to create a beat board in 
	which the user can activate specific sounds based on the
	button or key pressed.
	
*******************************************************************
Modules Used:
	1. tkinter
	2. playsound
	3. Thread from threading
	
*******************************************************************
Intructions to run script:

	1. Change directory to beat board directory: cd Beat-Board
	2. To execute run python command: python3 beatBoard.py

*******************************************************************
Usage:
	In order to use the following program, the user can either 
	1. Left click the following buttons 
	2. Press keys to activate the sounds
	
*******************************************************************
Key Press Layout: 
	The following keys correspond to the positions of the pads
			q	w	e
			a	s	d	
			z	x	c
			
*******************************************************************
	
